posting_body: ['Hawthorne Hill Apartments', '11801 York Street, Thornton, CO, 80233', 'More unit details at:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Welcome home to Hawthorne Hill', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 970 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'A NEW EDITION OF RENTAL LUXURY.', 'Hawthorne Hill beckons those who desire spacious living, a great location and luxurious amenities.', 'Exquisite finishes abound with nine-foot ceilings and crown molding accents, to optional cozy fireplaces and built-in desks.', "To make your life more enjoyable, we've included a fully equipped fitness center, resort-style pool and spa, and an elaborate clubroom.", 'Quick access to I-25 puts you within minutes of downtown and DIA is an easy drive away.', 'Features', '- Ceiling Fan', '- Balcony', '- Cable Ready', '- Dishwasher', '- Refrigerator', '- Washer & Dryer', 'In Unit', '- Garbage Disposal', '- Garden Tub', '- Air Conditioning', '- Microwave', '- View', '- Fireplace', '- Oversized Closets', 'Community Amenities', '- On Site Patrol', '- On Site Maintenance', '- Pet Friendly', '- Wireless Internet Access', '- Swimming Pool', '- Public Transportation', '- Business Center', '- Pet Park', '- Clubhouse', '- Playground', '- Trail, Bike, Hike, Jog', '- High Speed Internet Access', '- Individual Leases', '- Garage', '- Fitness Center', '- On Site Management', '- Extra Storage', '- Hot Tub', '- Emergency Maintenance', '- Accepts Electronic Payments', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Friendly*', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'MqxvjocVD9P']
